{"type":"article_comment","id":163227,"parentType":"article","parentId":10927,"uid":15246,"contents":"我自我定位為中國大陸的“中產”，能夠又條件翻牆上品蔥的絕大多數也屬於“中產階級”；<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/wlSgwLm.gif \" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wlSgwLm.gif \" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/wlSgwLm.gif \" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n發現其實在3-4線城市只拿初中文憑的年輕人是很多的，估計能接受高等教育的年輕人不到5%；<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/gnoamzv.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/gnoamzv.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/gnoamzv.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n說實話我很少接觸樓主提到的所謂底層，很難判斷他們的狀態，而且每個人的遭遇都不一樣，想法也不一樣，不好以偏概全去下結論。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/P8IQNgD.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/P8IQNgD.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/P8IQNgD.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-12-14","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}